reviewText:
A good expansion to a great game. Its nice that theres a second campaign where you can fight as the chaos and Orks. However the other campaign where you fight as Elder and Imperial guards is good if you want a bit of a challenge.

Everyone knows Guardmen are weak, crap and pretty much just there to make up some numbers. Well as you'd expect the game throws you against Chaos straight away and its a bit of a grind to beat them, so yeah, thats pretty annoying.

Still worth buying :}

i recommend this expansion :}
